                     <interp inst="t18370612-1441-offence-1" type="offenceSubcategory" value="simpleLarceny"></interp> for stealing, on the <rs id="t18370612-cd-42" type="crimeDate">
                        <join result="offenceCrimeDate" targOrder="Y" targets="t18370612-1441-offence-1 t18370612-cd-42"></join>25th of May</rs>, 2 pewter pots, value 4<hi rend="italic">s</hi>., the goods of <persName id="t18370612-name-356" type="victimName">
